<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="202" type="biology_ecology">
<paragraph blockId="5.[113,1089,1237,1614]" pageId="5" pageNumber="202">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[113,205,1237,1261]" pageId="5" pageNumber="202">Biology.</emphasis>
Adults: wingspan 
<quantity box="[409,524,1237,1261]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.8" metricValueMax="2.0" metricValueMin="1.6" pageId="5" pageNumber="202" unit="mm" value="18.0" valueMax="20.0" valueMin="16.0">16-20 mm</quantity>
. Adults fly from July to September; in north-eastern 
<collectingRegion box="[113,175,1269,1293]" country="Italy" name="Sicilia" pageId="5" pageNumber="202">Sicily</collectingRegion>
we observed adults from June to September. It flies among grass at dusk; our specimens were captured at light during the night. Larval host plant: probably monophagous on 
<taxonomicName box="[113,327,1335,1358]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Plantaginaceae" genus="Misopates" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="5" pageNumber="202" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="orontium">
<emphasis box="[113,327,1335,1358]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="202">Misopates orontium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(L.) Rafin. (
<taxonomicName box="[459,649,1333,1357]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Scrophulariaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="5" pageNumber="202" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Scrophulariaceae</taxonomicName>
).
</paragraph>
