<subSubSection lastPageId="6" lastPageNumber="203" pageId="5" pageNumber="202" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="5.[113,1089,1237,1614]" lastBlockId="6.[151,1127,219,500]" lastPageId="6" lastPageNumber="203" pageId="5" pageNumber="202">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[113,206,1430,1454]" pageId="5" pageNumber="202">Remark</emphasis>
. In the Italian checklist (
<bibRefCitation author="ARENBERGER E. &amp; GAEDIKE R. &amp; SCHOLZ A. &amp; ZANGHERI S." box="[483,743,1429,1454]" pageId="5" pageNumber="202" refId="ref4713" refString="ARENBERGER E., GAEDIKE R., SCHOLZ A. &amp; ZANGHERI S. 1995: Lepidoptera Urodoidea, Schreckensteinioidea, Epermenioidea, Alucitoidea, Pterophoroidea, Copromorphoidea. In: MINELLI A., RUFFO S. &amp; LA POSTA S. (eds.): Checklist delle specie della fauna italiana. Vol. 86. Calderini, Bologna, 13 pp." type="book" year="1995">ARENBERGER et al. 1995</bibRefCitation>
), 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Schawerda" authorityYear="1933" box="[764,904,1431,1454]" class="Insecta" family="Pterophoridae" genus="Stenoptilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="202" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="grisescens">
<emphasis box="[764,904,1431,1454]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="202">S. grisescens</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is indicated as a synonym of 
<taxonomicName authority="(Zeller, 1847)" baseAuthorityName="Zeller" baseAuthorityYear="1847" box="[247,485,1461,1486]" class="Insecta" family="Pterophoridae" genus="Stenoptilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="202" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="arida">
<emphasis box="[247,331,1463,1486]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="202">S. arida</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="ZELLER P. C." box="[345,477,1461,1486]" pageId="5" pageNumber="202" pagination="895 - 910" refId="ref5809" refString="ZELLER P. C. 1847: Bemerkungen uber die auf einer Reise nach Italien und Sicilien beobachteten Schmetterlingsarten. Isis von Oken 40: 895 - 910." type="journal article" year="1847">Zeller, 1847</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
(
<typeStatus box="[499,546,1462,1486]" pageId="5" pageNumber="202">type</typeStatus>
locality: Messina); the latter species is widespread in the entire peninsula and on the islands. 
<bibRefCitation author="BIGOT L. &amp; PICARD J." box="[569,819,1494,1518]" pageId="5" pageNumber="202" pagination="301 - 311" refId="ref5052" refString="BIGOT L. &amp; PICARD J. 2002: Les Stenoptilia de la section grisescens en France. Stenoptilia mariaeluisae nov. sp. et Stenoptilia inopinata nov. sp. Alexanor 21 (5) (2000): 301 - 311." type="journal article" year="2002">BIGOT &amp; PICARD (2002)</bibRefCitation>
considered 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Schawerda" authorityYear="1933" box="[950,1088,1495,1518]" class="Insecta" family="Pterophoridae" genus="Stenoptilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="202" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="grisescens">
<emphasis box="[950,1088,1495,1518]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="202">S. grisescens</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as a valid species and gave a key to identify the species belonging to the 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Schawerda" authorityYear="1933" box="[907,1018,1527,1550]" class="Insecta" family="Pterophoridae" genus="Stenoptilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="202" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="grisescens">
<emphasis box="[907,1018,1527,1550]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="202">grisescens</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
group (
<taxonomicName authorityName="Schawerda" authorityYear="1933" box="[122,262,1559,1582]" class="Insecta" family="Pterophoridae" genus="Stenoptilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="202" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="grisescens">
<emphasis box="[122,262,1559,1582]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="202">S. grisescens</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="Bigot &amp; Picard, 2002" authorityName="Bigot &amp; Picard" authorityYear="2002" box="[278,693,1557,1582]" class="Insecta" family="Pterophoridae" genus="Stenoptilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="202" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mariaeluisae">
<emphasis box="[278,446,1559,1582]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="202">S. mariaeluisae</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="BIGOT L. &amp; PICARD J." box="[455,693,1557,1582]" pageId="5" pageNumber="202" pagination="301 - 311" refId="ref5052" refString="BIGOT L. &amp; PICARD J. 2002: Les Stenoptilia de la section grisescens en France. Stenoptilia mariaeluisae nov. sp. et Stenoptilia inopinata nov. sp. Alexanor 21 (5) (2000): 301 - 311." type="journal article" year="2002">Bigot &amp; Picard, 2002</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="Bigot &amp; Picard, 2002" authorityName="Bigot &amp; Picard" authorityYear="2002" box="[706,1085,1557,1582]" class="Insecta" family="Pterophoridae" genus="Stenoptilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="202" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="inopinata">
<emphasis box="[706,837,1559,1582]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="202">S. inopinata</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="BIGOT L. &amp; PICARD J." box="[847,1085,1557,1582]" pageId="5" pageNumber="202" pagination="301 - 311" refId="ref5052" refString="BIGOT L. &amp; PICARD J. 2002: Les Stenoptilia de la section grisescens en France. Stenoptilia mariaeluisae nov. sp. et Stenoptilia inopinata nov. sp. Alexanor 21 (5) (2000): 301 - 311." type="journal article" year="2002">Bigot &amp; Picard, 2002</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, and 
<taxonomicName authority="Gibeaux, 1985" authorityName="Gibeaux" authorityYear="1985" box="[160,576,1589,1614]" class="Insecta" family="Pterophoridae" genus="Stenoptilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="202" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="gallobritannidactyla">
<emphasis box="[160,406,1591,1614]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="202">S. gallobritannidactyla</emphasis>
Gibeaux, 1985
</taxonomicName>
); the key is based on the characters of the male uncus and the ostium bursae and post-vaginal lamella of females. However, 
<bibRefCitation author="GIELIS C." box="[982,1127,220,244]" pageId="6" pageNumber="203" refId="ref5176" refString="GIELIS C. 2003: Pterophoridea &amp; Alucitoidea (Lepidoptera). In: VAN DER WOLF H. (ed.): World Catalogue of Insects. Vol. 4. Apollo Books, Stenstrup, 198 pp." type="book" year="2003">GIELIS (2003)</bibRefCitation>
still indicated 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Schawerda" authorityYear="1933" box="[301,439,253,276]" class="Insecta" family="Pterophoridae" genus="Stenoptilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="203" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="grisescens">
<emphasis box="[301,439,253,276]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="203">S. grisescens</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as a synonym of 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Zeller" baseAuthorityYear="1847" box="[624,708,253,276]" class="Insecta" family="Pterophoridae" genus="Stenoptilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="203" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="arida">
<emphasis box="[624,708,253,276]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="203">S. arida</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. 
<bibRefCitation author="ARENBERGER E." box="[719,927,251,276]" pageId="6" pageNumber="203" refId="ref4880" refString="ARENBERGER E. 2005: Pterophoridae III (Platyptiliini, Stenoptilia). In: GAEDIKE R. (ed.): Microlepidoptera Palaearctica. Vol. 12. Goecke &amp; Evers, Keltern, 191 pp." type="book" year="2005">ARENBERGER (2005)</bibRefCitation>
agreed with 
<bibRefCitation author="BIGOT L. &amp; PICARD J." pageId="6" pageNumber="203" pagination="301 - 311" refId="ref5052" refString="BIGOT L. &amp; PICARD J. 2002: Les Stenoptilia de la section grisescens en France. Stenoptilia mariaeluisae nov. sp. et Stenoptilia inopinata nov. sp. Alexanor 21 (5) (2000): 301 - 311." type="journal article" year="2002">BIGOT &amp; PICARD (2002)</bibRefCitation>
in considering 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Schawerda" authorityYear="1933" box="[497,635,285,308]" class="Insecta" family="Pterophoridae" genus="Stenoptilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="203" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="grisescens">
<emphasis box="[497,635,285,308]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="203">S. grisescens</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
a valid species, and confirmed its presence in 
<collectingCountry box="[151,200,315,339]" name="Italy" pageId="6" pageNumber="203">Italy</collectingCountry>
in 
<collectingRegion box="[230,335,315,339]" country="Italy" name="Piemonte" pageId="6" pageNumber="203">Piedmont</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingRegion box="[344,424,315,339]" country="Italy" name="Lazio" pageId="6" pageNumber="203">Latium</collectingRegion>
, and 
<collectingRegion box="[476,568,315,339]" country="Italy" name="Sardegna" pageId="6" pageNumber="203">Sardinia</collectingRegion>
. 
<bibRefCitation author="TREMATERRA P. &amp; BIGOT L. &amp; PICARD J." box="[576,835,315,339]" pageId="6" pageNumber="203" pagination="127 - 141" refId="ref5742" refString="TREMATERRA P., BIGOT L. &amp; PICARD J. 2006: Lepidoptera Pterophoridae dell'Italia centro-meridionale e insulare. Bollettino di Zoologia Agraria e di Bachicoltura, Ser. II 38: 127 - 141." type="journal article" year="2006">TREMATERRA et al. (2006)</bibRefCitation>
reported 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Schawerda" authorityYear="1933" box="[934,1070,317,340]" class="Insecta" family="Pterophoridae" genus="Stenoptilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="203" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="grisescens">
<emphasis box="[934,1070,317,340]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="203">S. grisescens</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from 
<collectingRegion box="[151,225,347,371]" country="Italy" name="Molise" pageId="6" pageNumber="203">Molise</collectingRegion>
and considered it by mistake as a new record for 
<collectingCountry box="[747,798,347,371]" name="Italy" pageId="6" pageNumber="203">Italy</collectingCountry>
. 
<bibRefCitation author="ARENBERGER E." box="[805,1013,347,372]" pageId="6" pageNumber="203" refId="ref4880" refString="ARENBERGER E. 2005: Pterophoridae III (Platyptiliini, Stenoptilia). In: GAEDIKE R. (ed.): Microlepidoptera Palaearctica. Vol. 12. Goecke &amp; Evers, Keltern, 191 pp." type="book" year="2005">ARENBERGER (2005)</bibRefCitation>
confirmed the presence of 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Zeller" baseAuthorityYear="1847" box="[324,410,381,404]" class="Insecta" family="Pterophoridae" genus="Stenoptilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="203" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="arida">
<emphasis box="[324,410,381,404]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="203">S. arida</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in 
<collectingRegion box="[447,527,379,403]" country="Italy" name="Lazio" pageId="6" pageNumber="203">Latium</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingRegion box="[538,617,379,403]" country="Italy" name="Liguria" pageId="6" pageNumber="203">Liguria</collectingRegion>
and 
<collectingRegion box="[672,736,379,403]" country="Italy" name="Sicilia" pageId="6" pageNumber="203">Sicily</collectingRegion>
. However, most of the records of 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Zeller" baseAuthorityYear="1847" class="Insecta" family="Pterophoridae" genus="Stenoptilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="203" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="arida">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="203">S. arida</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from 
<collectingCountry box="[276,325,411,435]" name="Italy" pageId="6" pageNumber="203">Italy</collectingCountry>
should be verified. Our data demonstrate the presence of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Schawerda" authorityYear="1933" box="[959,1098,413,436]" class="Insecta" family="Pterophoridae" genus="Stenoptilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="203" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="grisescens">
<emphasis box="[959,1098,413,436]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="203">S. grisescens</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in 
<collectingRegion box="[151,217,443,467]" country="Italy" name="Sicilia" pageId="6" pageNumber="203">Sicily</collectingRegion>
; the characters of the genitalia for both males and females are as described by 
<bibRefCitation author="NEL J." pageId="6" pageNumber="203" pagination="1 - 61" refId="ref5585" refString="NEL J. 2003: Atlas des Lepidopteres Pterophoridae de France. Revue de l'Association Roussillonnaise d'Entomologie 12 (Suppl.): 1 - 61." type="journal article" year="2003">NEL (2003)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="ARENBERGER E." box="[273,484,475,500]" pageId="6" pageNumber="203" refId="ref4880" refString="ARENBERGER E. 2005: Pterophoridae III (Platyptiliini, Stenoptilia). In: GAEDIKE R. (ed.): Microlepidoptera Palaearctica. Vol. 12. Goecke &amp; Evers, Keltern, 191 pp." type="book" year="2005">ARENBERGER (2005)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
